name: Stable Diffusion Magic Fantasy Forest
description:
This is my first model ever, please be kind :-)

It's a LoRA I created with over 100 images I'd created some time ago using another base model (unfortunately I don't remember which one hence me creating this so I don't lose the art style).

This works best with a weighting of 0.5 or less, Euler a, 30 sampling steps.

Some examples using revAnimated_v122 with this LoRA are as follows - hope you like it :)
